{
  "stem": "5740.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the middle there was a, a big, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] a round thing that everybody could, could do their business in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, like a bucket.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember the bucket was always full in the night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I could hear how, how it was dripping out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe out of seven nights a week, five nights a week, I was taking this bucket out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't stand it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when we came home, we had to work hard scrubbing the floors, bringing the coal, peeling the potatoes, of which we-- the soup was made, just of the, of the peels of the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I thought that in the whole world, there isn't enough bread that I can ever be satisfied.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was dreaming of potatoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At this time at the beginning, I still was getting-- I, I forgot to tell you this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is most important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was getting letters from my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she knew that you were in Ober Altstadt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the camp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wrote to my-- of course, I wrote.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was still a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There wasn't a concentration camp yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in that I wrote to my-- I wrote to her, but the first letter I got from my mother, and she say that she, she's ashamed to go on the street because people are laughing at what a stupid daughter she had.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Her daughter was freed to go home from the concentration-- from, from the [NON-ENGLISH] and all the people which stayed in the orphanage, they'll be freed any day.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, I felt terrible, first of all that my mother was so upset.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
